data.description:
MOTIVATED SELLER Welcomes YOU Home to The ENCLAVE in Nolanville!

 Did someone say, INCENTIVES? The seller is offering $5,000 at closing to be applied as an INTEREST RATE BUYDOWN OR WHATEVER THE BUYER NEEDS THE FUNDS FOR !

You'll feel instantly at home when you walk thru the front door of this ONLY 2 YEAR OLD- STYLECRAFT beautiful home. Sitting pretty on a BIG CORNER LOT with nice fenced in back yard, this home has 4 bedrooms, 2 1/2 baths, A 3 CAR GARAGE and oh so many lovely features throughout!  

 This home screams BRIGHT & CLEAN when you enter the front foyer, and it's open and roomy for entertaining  family or friends!

You'll be the envy of the neighborhood with the gorgeous, exotic granite bar which seats 4 or 5 easily, and makes for a perfect buffet line  on the holidays.

Bathrooms boast modern ceramic tile throughout in a lovely shade of light gray with a marble white effect throughout, as well as the Primary has that soaking bathtub you will love to come home to.

The owner's tasteful style and MANY UPGRADES THROUGHOUT won't disappoint!
